imdb.plot outline: What sort people are proud of an insult? What's wrong with them? The answer ... nothing!!! They are bikers -and there's nothing wrong with them. They love the exhilaration and challenge of riding Australia's roads. They understand the nuances of the various motorcycle tribes.Most Australians are ignorant of the passion they share with hundreds of thousands of other motorcycling Aussies. This ignorance shows itself in insults and negative stereotyping. Like most Aussies they take this in their stride and take pride in being regarded with disdain. They are -Temporary Australians and proud of it!
